WRT activities, I added [an example](https://www.figma.com/design/K9BTJ3aZAvwWBXU9N8aqGa/-27983-Fleet-Desktop-%3E-Self-service--Add-%22Update%22-actions-when-updates-are-detected-for-installed-so?node-id=5318-3291&t=LPfejWpLp8jclkAm-11) to the ticket above.

